@startuml Gesture_Input_Activity_States
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam state {
    BackgroundColor #E1F5FE
    BorderColor #01579B
}

[*] --> Initializing : onCreate()

Initializing --> WaitingForGesture : Setup Complete

WaitingForGesture --> Drawing : User Starts Drawing
Drawing --> GestureDrawn : Drawing Complete

GestureDrawn --> Recognizing : Process Gesture
Recognizing --> Matching : Match Against Saved Gestures

Matching --> GestureMatched : Match Found
Matching --> GestureNotMatched : No Match Found

GestureMatched --> ExecutingFunction : Execute Bound Function
ExecutingFunction --> FunctionExecuted : Function Complete
FunctionExecuted --> MainScreen : Navigate to MainActivity

GestureNotMatched --> WaitingForGesture : Try Again

WaitingForGesture --> MainScreen : Skip Gesture Login

MainScreen --> [*] : Activity Finished

@enduml
